 order in a low frequency and momentum\nexpansion in general dimensions, in addition to determining explicit results\nfor two dimensional holographic CFT environments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Apr 2020 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 7 Jun 2020 20:05:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 29 Jul 2020 18:41:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
