 stellar\nmass within a 1-2 Myr old cluster: a slightly super-linear scaling between the\ngas accretion rate and stellar mass ($\\dot{M}\\propto M_\\star^{1.4}$), a\nslightly super-linear scaling between the gas disc mass and the stellar mass\n($M_\\mathrm{g}\\propto M_\\star^{1.4}$) and a super-linear relation between the\ndust disc mass and stellar mass ($M_\\mathrm{d}\\propto M_\\star^{1.4-4.1}$).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Apr 2020 18:09:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Sep 2020 09:05:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-30"}
