essed versions of them. We show that the\n1stepVQA model outperforms other VQA models in this scenario. We are providing\nthe dedicated new database free of charge at\nhttps://live.ece.utexas.edu/research/onestep/index.html\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Apr 2020 19:06:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-15"}
