s and near-optimal performance of the proposed\nstatistical CSI aided RE optimization approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2020 02:53:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 May 2020 06:55:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-11"}
