toichiometric chalcogenide compound under ORR\nconditions. This study shows while PtTe2 is stable and highly useful for HER,\nthis property does not apply to ORR, which undergoes a fundamentally different\nmechanism. This study broadens our knowledge of the electrocatalysis of TMDs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2020 08:40:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
