nding this, we propose a\nnew conjecture, and discuss some applications to the (real) Jacobian\nconjecture. We also consider the properness of more general maps $x\\pm (Ax)^k$\nor $x\\pm A(x^k)$. By a result of Druzkowski, our results can be applied to all\npolynomial self-mappings of $\\mathbb{C}^m$ or $\\mathbb{R}^m$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2020 12:24:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Apr 2020 17:11:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 20 Apr 2020 02:51:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-21"}
