\circ$ shocks producing the largest number of protons with energies at least\na few times the thermal energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Apr 2020 15:14:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Jun 2020 16:53:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-15"}
